{"tid":464130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一講家用就知老母幾撚黑暗","createTime":"2017-11-10T08:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T15:37:16.000Z","uid":58841,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"34e76069adb5c8e5bbd30c9495817d308d8eeec5","tid":464130,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:31:22.000Z","msg":"事關我就做緊pt sales <br />\n每個月多數得6-7000 生意好+多更先去到9000<br />\n咁我照實報數老母就問我拎家用<br />\n但係我要交雜費同搭車食飯已經無錢剩<br />\n咁我呢兩個月無俾家用 佢就開始當我透明 成日比說話我聽<br />\n琴日我就係我銀行拎1000俾佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿 我得返300蚊頂成個月你開心未<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （無出聲）又話當初俾一半 而家得1000把鬼呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我每個月得5000比左一半你我搭車食飯邊有錢呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你之前又話有7000<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我唔係個個月都有咁多架<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你有7000要俾4000呀同你講<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我問fd同同事佢地都係俾一兩千炸 全職仲要得三四千 你咁樣係咪想玩死我呀<br />\n<br />\n聽到個下覺得佢真係好撚離譜<br />\n嬲嬲下諗起以前佢都無俾零用錢我（老豆俾）<br />\n到大學每日得50蚊食飯 有時唔夠錢要問老豆拎<br />\n細個買既衫褲鞋襪呀電腦個d都係姑媽送<br />\n<br />\n之後我玩電腦唔理佢 老豆就走入黎同我講俾幾千老母 佢會資助返我一兩千<br />\n個陣真係一路聽佢講一路喊<br />\n以前好憎老豆 但係呢種時候我覺得佢係真正明白我既處境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeb59467ee656272086767737fd7d3a27b7d4cf","tid":464130,"uid":65629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e8276a513b9787b86009a798bfb7e38fc96ed02","tid":464130,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD老豆老母真係以為個物價仲係幾十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ede9e406be033c8081295b5a681e534cb491436","tid":464130,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:37:28.000Z","msg":"你老豆幾好"},{"pid":"07dc27a51f0098a02c2359df7fa82707e00c14df","tid":464130,"uid":65629,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD老豆老母真係以為個物價仲係幾十年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd24fffa56c0d976d3a57ddca81995c86c2bc62","tid":464130,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"706eec58334c00e737b586049bcc2eb2b63b5bf5","tid":464130,"uid":65629,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca3e67b3787efee0e8ff60cfd7051f429f9a70c","tid":464130,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母都係咁<br />\n細個成日無端端俾佢鬧 日日受佢氣<br />\n有野就搵我救命 無野就當我出氣袋<br />\n佢生我似當我係個工具多過真係仔女"},{"pid":"853ff18f5422a98fa586f6750b09161103c97859","tid":464130,"uid":104659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:48:12.000Z","msg":"pt肯比都預唔多啦, 莫講話全職, 比3成都夠了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc0dc4658b54af68bc18f2bb713c80ddfce23d6","tid":464130,"uid":65893,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:50:14.000Z","msg":"PT做咩要比家用"},{"pid":"2439d67dc02d58cb714bdfd780bbb9edb0836c53","tid":464130,"uid":31979,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:51:15.000Z","msg":"屋企差人好多錢，一個月俾25k家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7474f5d0c9913315a4acf60f60076cddbeeed210","tid":464130,"uid":87973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:51:45.000Z","msg":"5000 / 2 = 2500<br />\n<br />\n當你一個月 翻二十日工 (PT應該更少)<br />\n車費來回 40蚊<br />\n窮食早餐 30蚊<br />\n窮食午餐 35蚊 (帶飯可以更慳)<br />\n其他繳費 300蚊<br />\n<br />\n2500 - 800 - 1500 - 300 = 100<br />\n<br />\n窮果陣重有一百蚊已經好好啦"},{"pid":"fce5b98ba19162ef5937deec2261246e47a4fab7","tid":464130,"uid":60287,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:53:02.000Z","msg":"自從我老母開始懶到飯都唔煮我就一蚊家用都無比，我同佢講人工得一萬佢好意思叫我交五千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企唔洗交租，又冇經濟負擔，<br />\n老母又蠢，成日人地話點就點，洗腳唔抹腳，最慘係吓吓都死要面，對住人就闊佬，對住屋企人就度度縮縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我寧願自己收埋哂d錢，到第時真係要果陣先拎出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fa87414136d7decfe75d5b0c22c7aa7d877589","tid":464130,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5000 / 2 = 2500<br />\n<br />\n當你一個月 翻二十日工 (PT應該更少)<br />\n車費來回 40蚊<br />\n窮食早餐 30蚊<br />\n窮食午餐 35蚊 (帶飯可以更慳)<br />\n其他繳費 300蚊<br />\n<br />\n2500 - 800 - 1500 - 300 = 100<br />\n<br />\n窮果陣重有一百蚊已經好好啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n負一日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2807ab9d21a47995ee0a3d56ef1177cfef50056c","tid":464130,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817df54a41fcbc5e9220190ac40844c832728de4","tid":464130,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"如果無我問返佢拎錢啦pt得雞碎咁多夠邊個洗<br />\n依家d細路真係渣"},{"pid":"59f8977672a7aae196345900ba46d2e7515cca6a","tid":464130,"uid":87973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:56:35.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻 快D幫我改正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029ddec198bc5fcfc7874528f73ade9aaf8fb206","tid":464130,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5db69053c0815bd25a44d00202d80e8e6edd6884","tid":464130,"uid":120093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"今晚同佢講話比人炒左以後無錢俾"},{"pid":"8e12ce25ef90ad8af963ee894c24650c96a5dc08","tid":464130,"uid":37708,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"隨著北野武的日益走紅，母親佐紀公然向北野武索取每個月20萬日元的零花錢，北野武因此痛駡母親為吸血鬼。他對貪婪的母親、對家，埋怨、憤怒乃至失望了。<br />\n但就像北野武的電影結局，結局來得有點突然。母親去世後，留給北野武兩份遺物：一封信和一本存摺。信中寫道：「我兒，你從小生性放蕩，我擔心你日後一無所有&hellip;&hellip;存摺裡有一千萬圓。」而存摺裡便是高達一千萬圓的存款。原來母親向他要的每一筆錢，她一分沒花，全都存起來。因為，她比誰都愛北野武，擔心他一日人氣全無會變得一無所有。<br />\n沒有人比貧窮的女人和媽媽，更知道生活的苦，貪婪的背後是悲傷的愛。"},{"pid":"c9ae3b798ee1dda5838551fca247e1c7de4220cf","tid":464130,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:05:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老母都係咁<br />\n細個成日無端端俾佢鬧 日日受佢氣<br />\n有野就搵我救命 無野就當我出氣袋<br />\n佢生我似當我係個工具多過真係仔女</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你 exactly <br />\n成日話生女好過生仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3036c327dd6013a6e2ad65b501278c131bbc7c1d","tid":464130,"uid":72118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"900c1ddc85b1377c49464c7564aacc15ef432436","tid":464130,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"大學都要問屋企攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"328999ceee58c31c6884d401d52ce9d759a28fa8","tid":464130,"uid":44322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係一樣米養百樣人，月薪2皮都係畀5千家用，老母仲問我夠唔夠洗，我阿媽真係太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n14k本身俾3.5k,老母把口成日都提住錢，但其實我知佢心底都係想我唔好咁大洗，成日話如果你想pt讀返書就唔使俾家用專心去讀。呢排知道屋企等錢用，幾個月前加到5k俾佢，都俾得心甘情願。<br />\n所以老母點對你，你點對返佢就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d58472b5357624ef524def821238abd035b2c0","tid":464130,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T09:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大學都要問屋企攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣好多堂無野做<br />\n去到final year先開始做pt"}]}